{"synckey":1687370810,"updated":[{"bookId":"520497","bookmarkId":"520497_7_1622-1726","chapterUid":94,"markText":"爱情的可贵之处，除了浪漫、美好之外，还有其更加珍贵的功能，就是在爱情的关系里，你拥有了一个成长的机会，所有在儿时没有成长好的人格特点，在爱情里，都能够再次获得成长的机会。也只有在爱情的关系里，才有这样的机会。","range":"1782-1886","createTime":1648357419,"type":1},{"bookId":"520497","bookmarkId":"520497_7_741-823","chapterUid":94,"markText":"真实的情况是，只要你自己内心强大、人格完整、心中充满爱、拥有爱的能力，有很多人是适合你的对象，不是一个人，而是一群人。与这群人中的任何一个结合，你都可能会获得幸福。","range":"741-823","createTime":1648357398,"type":1}],"removed":[],"chapters":[{"title":"有爱的能力，幸福不是神话","chapterUid":94,"chapterIdx":8}],"book":{"bookId":"520497","version":458632911,"format":"epub","soldout":1,"bookStatus":1,"cover":"https://cdn.weread.qq.com/weread/cover/15/YueWen_520497/s_YueWen_520497.jpg","title":"爱的五种能力","author":"赵永久","coverBoxInfo":{"blurhash":"KESYBau1tQ-Lf|kQqDacxt","colors":[{"key":"1/4","hex":"#360e19"},{"key":"1/6","hex":"#3f0218"},{"key":"1/8","hex":"#470019"},{"key":"2/4","hex":"#4d2528"},{"key":"2/6","hex":"#571d25"},{"key":"2/8","hex":"#620e22"},{"key":"3/4","hex":"#693b39"},{"key":"3/6","hex":"#743333"},{"key":"3/8","hex":"#80292c"},{"key":"3/12","hex":"#950020"},{"key":"4/6","hex":"#8f4d49"},{"key":"4/10","hex":"#a63c3b"},{"key":"4/4","hex":"#825451"},{"key":"5/10","hex":"#c45751"},{"key":"5/4","hex":"#9b6e6a"},{"key":"5/8","hex":"#b7605a"},{"key":"6/4","hex":"#b58984"},{"key":"6/6","hex":"#c4827b"},{"key":"6/8","hex":"#d27c73"},{"key":"6/12","hex":"#ec6b62"},{"key":"7/8","hex":"#ef958c"},{"key":"7/10","hex":"#fd8e83"},{"key":"7/12","hex":"#ff8579"},{"key":"8/4","hex":"#ebbdb7"},{"key":"8/6","hex":"#fcb7ae"},{"key":"8/12","hex":"#ff9c8e"},{"key":"9/2","hex":"#f1dfdc"},{"key":"9/12","hex":"#ffb5a9"},{"key":"1/100","hex":"#d27c73"},{"key":"2/100","hex":"#ef958c"},{"key":"3/100","hex":"#ffffff"},{"key":"4/100","hex":"#F3E8E5"},{"key":"5/100","hex":"#F3E8E5"},{"key":"6/100","hex":"#270500"}],"dominate_color":{"hex":"#fae1dd","hsv":[9.129544704614,11.673609570208866,98.12600453427234]},"custom_cover":"https:/